.TH THEMIS 1 "May 2026" "Themis 0.1.3" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
themis \- run the Project Themis service manager
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B themis
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B themis
starts the Project Themis server. The service initializes DBus communication,
loads Project Themis runtime files, starts configured plugins, and exposes the
Project Themis HTTP API.
.PP
On Debian systems this program is normally managed through
.BR systemd (1)
using
.BR themis.service .
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR systemctl (1),
.BR dbus-daemon (1)
